<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>经典贪吃蛇小游戏</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>

    <div class="game-container">
        <h1>贪吃蛇大作战</h1>
        
        <div class="score-board">
            <div class="score-box">当前得分: <span id="current-score">0</span></div>
            <div class="score-box">最高纪录: <span id="high-score">0</span></div>
        </div>

        <div class="canvas-wrapper">
            <canvas id="gameCanvas" width="400" height="400"></canvas>
            
            <div id="overlay" class="overlay hidden">
                <div class="overlay-content">
                    <h2 id="overlay-title">游戏结束</h2>
                    <p>最终得分: <span id="final-score">0</span></p>
                    <button id="start-btn">重新开始</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="instructions">
            <p>使用键盘方向键 <span class="key">↑</span> <span class="key">↓</span> <span class="key">←</span> <span class="key">→</span> 控制移动</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
